										<div class="accordion-content">
											<p>Apple&nbsp;TV+ is an all-new streaming service from Apple. Watch original shows and films, ad-free and on demand, in 4K HDR and Dolby Atmos sound.</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</li>
								<li id="eligible-devices" class="accordion-item" data-accordion-item>
									<div class="header-wrapper">
										<h3 class="accordion-headline typography-eyebrow">Which devices are eligible to receive one free year of Apple&nbsp;TV+?</h3>
										<button class="icon icon-plus" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-panel-2" aria-labelledby="accordion-label-2">
									</button>
									</div>
									<div class="accordion-panel" id="accordion-panel-2" aria-hidden="true">
										<div class="accordion-content">
											<p>Your free year of Apple&nbsp;TV+ is included when you buy a new iPhone, iPad, iPod touch, Apple&nbsp;TV, or Mac after September 10, 2019, from Apple or an Apple-authorized reseller. Your new device must also be capable of running the latest iOS, iPadOS, tvOS, or macOS.</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</li>
								<li id="how-to-activate-my-free-subscription" class="accordion-item" data-accordion-item>
