										<button class="icon icon-plus" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-panel-3" aria-labelledby="accordion-label-3">
									</button>
									</div>
									<div class="accordion-panel" id="accordion-panel-3" aria-hidden="true">
										<div class="accordion-content">
											<p>You can activate your free Apple&nbsp;TV+ subscription after you set up your new Apple device. Simply follow the steps outlined above. Or visit <a href="https://support.apple.com/kb/HT210627">support.apple.com</a> for more information.</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</li>
								<li id="when-does-my-offer-expire" class="accordion-item" data-accordion-item>
